{"type":"answer","id":7363,"parentType":"question","parentId":1690,"uid":6,"contents":"首先个人对「支那」一词其实是并不反对的，但是「支豚」这种明显贬义就是另一回事了。<br>\n<br>\n那么有好些大手子呢，作为大手子口中的「支豚」，却不承认自己是「支豚」，我暂且蒙在鼓里。<br>\n<br>\n（当然某大手子团体也把自己画为支豚，那还真是触啊）<br>\n<br>\n是不是除了中国壬都是高雅壬呢？隐隐约约觉得不对啊。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537689012235822.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537689012235822.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537689012235822.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n你日特有的精神胜利法，难道日本壬就没有随地小便的吗？QQQXX，，，<br>\n<br>\n～I'm in a temper!!!～<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537688308499620.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537688308499620.png\" alt=\"https://mhimg.github.io/ueditor/20180923/1537688308499620.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n某高雅人士提到了 INM。<br>\n<br>\n我们知道 INM≈网络暴力（确信），那么您日真是太高雅了，，，","date":"2018-09-23","agreeCount":4,"discussionCount":0}